Lingua-YaTeA version 0.1
================================

(Yet Another Term ExtrActor)

YaTeA is a module implrementing a configurable term extractor. It 
detecting term candidates in corpora. It can also take into account
testified terms issued from terminological resources.

Contains this script :

    yatea

(see MANIFEST for all the files)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Or if you don't have the "make" program:

   perl Build.PL
   Build
   Build test
   Build install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Pod::Usage
 Getopt::Long
 Config::General >= 2.30
 Data::Dumper
 File::Path
 Parse::Yapp

DOCUMENTATION

Please see documentation Yatea_user_manual.pdf in the DOC
subdirectory.

